\v 3 Uzzi's¦190686 son was Yizrahyah. Yizrahyah's five sons were Mikael, Ovadyah, Yoel¦190692, and Yishiyah. They were all \add ≈leaders of their¦190696 clans\add*.
\v 4 Along with them according to their \add ≈family records\add*, were 36,000 troops¦190702 in the army, because they¦190710 \add ≈had numerous\add* wives¦190711 and sons¦190712.
