\p
\v 28 \add This is a list of\add* \add ≈the cities and areas where Efrayim's descendants lived\add*: Beyt-El and the nearby villages, Naaran¦191014 to the east, Gezer¦191016 to the west and the nearby villages, and Shekem and the nearby villages extending \add north\add* as far as Ayyah¦191022 and its villages.
\p
\v 29 Along the border of the area where the descendants of Menashsheh¦191030 lived were these¦191041 towns: Beyt-Shan, Taanak, Megiddo¦191037, Dor¦191039, and all the nearby villages. The people who lived in all those places were descendants of Yakov's son Yosef¦191044 \add (Joseph)\add*.
