\v 16 Ovadyah (Shemayah's¦191794 son, Shemayah was Galal's¦191797 son, Galal was Yedutun's son), and Berekyah who lived in one of the villages¦191809 where the Netofat people lived (Berekyah was Asa's¦191804 son, Asa was Elkanah's¦191807 son).
\p
